Schenck et al., Respondents, v. Foley, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. January 16, 1890.) Apppal from city court, general term.

Argued before Larremore, O. J., and Bisohoff, J.

Jas. Kearney, for appellant. Wm. Stainton. for respondents.

No opinion. Ordered that the order appealed from be affirmed, with costs.
